.TH ALFACONF 5 "2026-04-19" "maneater-bench" "Maneater Bench Fixtures"
.SH NAME
alfaconf \- deterministic bench fixture config format number 1
.SH SYNOPSIS
.I ~/.config/maneater-bench/alfaconf.toml
.SH DESCRIPTION
This page describes bench fixture config format number 1. The format
is a TOML document whose shape varies per fixture so the embedding index
does not collapse across pages. Mandoc + pandoc must still render all
the usual sections (NAME, SYNOPSIS, DESCRIPTION, EXAMPLES, SEE ALSO)
per page.
.SH SYNTAX
.PP
Fields:
.TP
.B enabled
Boolean for fixture 1.
.TP
.B label
String label for fixture 1.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
.nf
.RS
enabled = true
label = "fixture-1"
.RE
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR maneater.toml (5)
